00:32:05.090 --> 00:32:06.390
Post the token to that.

00:32:06.390 --> 00:32:08.350
And then that token
can be posted to Google

00:32:08.350 --> 00:32:10.830
and authorized by
Google on your behalf.

00:32:10.830 --> 00:32:14.950
So again, just looking at that
