00:32:19.290 --> 00:32:21.100
They post the token
to the server.

00:32:21.100 --> 00:32:22.719
So now Google will
get the server,

00:32:22.719 --> 00:32:23.760
ACK it, and send it back.

00:32:23.760 --> 00:32:25.630
So we avoid the
bad guys doing it.

00:32:25.630 --> 00:32:28.192
Let's see what the code
